metisse: metisse (Metisse is an X-based window system)
metisse:
metisse: Xmetisse is a mix of Xvnc and XDarwin. It draws nothing on your
metisse: screen; everything is drawn into pixmaps. Similarly to Xvnc, but with
metisse: a different protocol, Xmetisse can send these pixmaps (and other
metisse: information) to a "viewer". FvwmCompositor is such a viewer; it uses
metisse: OpenGL for rendering the X desktop into a window of a "regular" 3D
metisse: accelerated X server.
metisse:
metisse: http://insitu.lri.fr/metisse/
metisse: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
